div.head: Description of changes for 2013.02
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft started from a copy of a transcription of the St. Victor manuscript. A trancription of the SSorbonne ms still needs to be completed. Corrections and additions will follow a collation comparision of available manuscript witnesses. Citations, cross-references, and a critical apparatus still need to be constructed.
